      <h2 class="text-xl font-light text-blue-400 mt-10 mb-4 border-l-4 border-blue-400 pl-4">Strategy Tips for FA Words</h2>

      <p>FA is the most versatile F-pair, starting hundreds of everyday words. FACTORY (15 pts) and FATHOM (14 pts) are your premium targets. FABRIC (13 pts), FAMOUS (11 pts), and FALCON (11 pts) use common consonants for reliable mid-game plays. Short FA words (FAD, FAN, FAR, FAT) score 6-9 points while clearing the 4-point F tile.</p>

      <div class="not-prose my-6 flex flex-wrap items-center justify-center gap-3">
        <span class="inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 px-3 py-1.5 rounded-lg bg-gray-800 border border-gray-700 text-sm"><span class="text-white font-bold">FOXHOUND</span><span class="text-blue-400 text-xs">21 pts</span></span>
        <span class="inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 px-3 py-1.5 rounded-lg bg-gray-800 border border-gray-700 text-sm"><span class="text-white font-bold">HALFWAY</span><span class="text-blue-400 text-xs">19 pts</span></span>
